current.quote_home_1: Vertty explores the untapped potential in everyday products
current.quote_home_2: VERTTY PRODUCTS IS NOT JUST ABOUT FULFILLING A PURPOSE. IT ALSO REPRESENTS A NEW STANCE IN LIFE, A DIFFERENT ANGLE..
current.essence_description_1:
Strong words. Stronger foundations.

When we set off to reinvent the beach towel, in 2013, these were our guiding lights, the beacons that kept us focused and decisive.

Today, they are synonyms to our name, and go hand in hand with what we do and have achieved.
current.essence_description_2:
We introduced ourselves with a refreshing take on an overlooked commodity. By injecting a much needed personality and character to a forsaken object, we showed the world that it is not what you do that matters, but how you do it.

We’ve since carried that insight into numerous projects, giving new life and purpose to stagnant products.

This is, and always will be, our way of life.
current.essence_description_3:
We rely heavily on creativity and imagination to keep us on our toes, but we depend even further on our passion and commitment to execution.

Great, meaningful and worthy execution, to be exact.

Not only do we aim to make your life better, we aim to make the world a safer and healthier place. That’s exactly why, since day one, we’ve made a point on using only the safest, most ecological and progressive means of manufacturing.

From our materials to production methods and suppliers, everything is deeply scrutinized to meet our standards, and most importantly, yours.
current.essence_description_4:
We started strong, and grew stronger.

Our unwavering passion and resolution took us from a fledgling beach towel company to an established global brand.

We’ve conquered the world, selling to every continent and ocean, building partnerships with numerous suppliers and distributors and teaming with up and coming athletes and lifestyle advocates.

But we want to do even more, reach even more. We mean to make Vertty an household name and a true companion to everyday life. We want to help you make the most of your time by taking the most time for what truly matters.

You.
current.worldwideShipping:
Express service delivered by DHL in 2 to 3 business days.
The non-priority service is delivered by the regular post office and is delivered in 5 to 10 business days.
current.feature_towel_text_1: c o l o r f u l
current.towel_description: Material composition: 90% Cotton 10% Polyester -  Larger size: 185 x 110 cm -  Lightweight: 620g
current.towel_concept:
Vertty reinvented the beach towel concept, taking the sophistication of the city to a casual setting.

We created a model exploring the full potential of a common object, turning a basic commodity into a trendy accessory.

With a unique design, lighter weight and larger size; with a fabric that dries up faster and presenting a waterproof pocket and a colorful variety, the Vertty towel is not just about fulfilling a purpose. It also represents a new stance in life, a different angle.

Things dont have to be just what they're supposed to. Vertty's team believes that even the ordinary can become distinct.

Because style is not a result of having money or status. Its about taste and attitude.
current.feature_backpack_text_1: the sand belongs to the beach
current.backpack_description: Material composition: 30% Neopren 10% Foam 30% Eva 30% Pollyester - Weight: 1.4kg
current.backpack_concept:
Made for everyday life, our backpack introduces an impressive number of versatile and distinctive features built to enhance transportation.

With its structured design and adaptive functionalities, the Vertty backpack is an inviting bridge between the carefully planned urban spirit with the demanding and impulsive thrill-seeking aspect of adventure.

Vertty is creating the best backpack ever, a high-quality, sophisticated accessory that embraces everyday urban life.

Durable enough to handle a day at the beach but stylish enough for city life, it’s more than meets the eye. The hard outer shell secures and protects, while water-resistant fabric and zippers keep your valuables dry. Though lightweight, the backpack has additional space for your board shorts and towel, you can pack for both a day in the city and at the beach. And an innovative, netted pocket on the bottom of the bag can be opened to release any unwanted sand.
